logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# OS files
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

